    <article>
        <p>This is the best TANK! game ever created. In the fantastically 80&#39;s vein of classic arcade games...TANK! is simple, fun and satisfying. Play someone else on your iPhone and relive all the fun that old skool video games used to be.</p>
<p>NOTE: This is a two player game only (on the same device), so be sure to bring a friend.</p>
<h3>TANK! for iPhone, iPod touch, and iPad on the iTunes App Store</h3>
<p><a href="http://itunes.apple.com/us/app/tank/id394804754?mt=8">http://itunes.apple.com/us/app/tank/id394804754?mt=8</a></p>

